item.title: Deb Fischer bio
item.description: Senator Deb Fischer Bio Senator Debra Strobel Fischer is an American politician. She has been serving as the senior U.S. Senator from Nebraska under the Republican since 2013. She was a member of the rural high school board of Education from 1990 to 2004. She also served two terms as a representative in the Nebraska Legislature. Fischer was born on March 1, 1951, in Lincoln, Nebraska. She studied at Lincoln Southeast High school.
